Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:06.45,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:06.45,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:12.79,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:12.79,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.51,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.51,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:39.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:39.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.72,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.72,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:50.26,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:50.26,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:56.50,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:56.50,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:01.84,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:01.84,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:07.55,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:07.55,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:11.32,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:11.32,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:32.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:35.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What nice weather...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:40.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although this light is already torturous...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:42.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, please close the curtain! I'm going to turn into sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:44.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see the screen...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:45.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:46.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(434,351)\c&H539AD0&}"Oh, this voice is...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:48.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! That totally woke me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:52.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Massages sure are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all the tired faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:56.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go get a massage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:01:58.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have discount tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:01.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's aim for another lively day of work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:01.98,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Monkel {\be1\3c&H000000&}is a pun on a Japanese energy drink called Yunkel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:04.31,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Discount tickets to a massage parlor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:07.36,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,AND a Monkel drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:11.57,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, she's drinking Monkel Royal, marketed\Nby the industry to people in their fifties...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:15.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:18.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(434,371)\c&H3F97D6&}"You're wonderful, Miwako-san ☆"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:19.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(434,331)\c&H4C98D2&}"You're very manly"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:21.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My goodness, what's the matter, Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:21.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(434,311)\c&H429AD9&}"That (7-3 split ☆) is very cool also"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:21.66,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\be1\shad0}The {\3c&H635514&\be0}7-3 split {\be1\3c&H000000&}is a stereotypical Japanese old man hairdo when\Nthey split 70% of their hair one way and 30% the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:25.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so these are what you made the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:27.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:28.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Nomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:30.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are dextrous for a first timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:34.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, your earlier work was better, Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:38.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wasn't in the groove that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you were too busy getting in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:42.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk with Yamada-san more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:45.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:49.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, she's, well, how should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A naïve girl, the type you don't see very often these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't make any moves on her unless you're serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:57.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that doesn't sound nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:03:00.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's totally treating us like germs. How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to say that much, then why\Ndon't you make an attack on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:07.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to me that she likes you, Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:06.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs26\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H4C98D2&\pos(405,91)}"Miwako-san,\N"Attack ☆" is an obsolete word"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:10.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you getting in our way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:13.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:16.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I've known her for a while, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:17.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a valid reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:18.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:21.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll make us some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:25.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada is like a precious friend to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:27.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you forget about that and just date her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:34.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You must like her as well, if you think of her as so precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:38.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't share a futon with Takemoto-kun forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:40.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We sleep in different futons!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:43.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiming for Rika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:51.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, if I was, I would've just stayed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:52.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was just part-time or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:04:00.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if that was the case, you wouldn't\Nhave quit Harada Designs to come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:02.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that an issue arose relating to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:06.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You got too close to Rika-san, things got uncomfortable,\Nand you couldn't stay around anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:07.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:10.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you trying to say, Yamazaki-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:15.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It wasn't like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please quit already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:29.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:32.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:34.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika-san is my idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:36.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, how dare you... when she's\Nbeen depressed about her husband...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Give up! I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:43.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:49.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you interfering with us when\Nyou're interested in somebody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:57.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even we could figure out Yamada-san's feelings,\Nso there's no way you haven't noticed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:02.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're not pushing her away, but rather, you're tormenting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:12.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's that you want to keep her "on the bench",\Nin case your first choice doesn't work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:24.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll take the unspoiled Yamada-san if Rika-san doesn't work out."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:28.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:29.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:32.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:38.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going straight home from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya-san, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear me, you should know already without me having to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:46.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Of course I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:48.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll ask anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:52.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You two! What about your assignments?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:52.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the book, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:56.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:57.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\bord1.5\fscx65\fs22\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H4C98D2&\pos(426,235)}"Miwako-san,\Nhey, feed me... ☆"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mayama. And Nomiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:04.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:09.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The photo shoot suddenly got bumped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:13.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of soon, but are the potteries from the other day finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that we came up without warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:17.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:19.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:23.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite an amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:25.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're everyone's presentations for the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,School festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for coming when you're so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:33.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I'm just helping everyone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:36.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:38.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Takemoto doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been going back to the apartment lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:44.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been running around looking for jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:48.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And every evening he comes back looking depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:53.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's obsessed with making some tower-like object...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! And how's Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:06:59.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.20,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx50\fsp7\fs48\c&HEAF1F7&\shad0\pos(431,57)}All sorts of deities currently visiting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:06.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All sorts of people are observing her everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:11.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little difficult for me to approach her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's still Hagu-chan on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:17.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure things will calm down once the Hamabi Festival ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:21.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but we still eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:27.68,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\fs15\fsp-0.5\fscx80\bord1\be1\c&H353934&\shad0\frx342\fry4\pos(432,376)\3c&H676D69&}Ceramics Second Department
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:25.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We bring the ingredients and cook them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:27.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.97,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I've graduated already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:33.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I cooked curry today! Have some with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:35.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:36.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Nomiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:37.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy... this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:46.87,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is the scent of chocolate wafting out of the curry...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:48.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-daa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the question of the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:54.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This special curry has a certain hidden ingredient\Nin it to give it more presence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.38,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not hidden at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:02.84,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, it's actually manifesting itself all over the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:03.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-daa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:05.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is: "chocolate"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:06.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:07.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, would you like to have some?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:08.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:09.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry about us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:11.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unfortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:18.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's your home cooking, Yamada-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:20.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to eat it even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:21.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:25.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:26.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's piercing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:28.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It wells up inside me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It surpasses my wildest expectations!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:34.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Piercing"? "Wells up"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:38.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are some dubious expressions, but\NI sense something sharp coming out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:43.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's wrap it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada, can you hold it up at that end?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:49.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really wrapping it up carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:52.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, these things have no replacements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:57.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mayama. That goes in B.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:08:59.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really hopeless, Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:03.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, you're so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the last of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:14.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Miwako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:16.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:19.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The model?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:25.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mayama. The leg on the desk\Nin the meeting room buckled...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:27.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So please come right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:31.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya-san, there's an emergency\Nsituation for the meeting at nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's being held at Yotsuya, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The train would be quicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:38.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:43.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you so amicably waving your hand with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:45.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? I get it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Mayama, he sure is persistent or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:06.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh oh, Mayama forgot his coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:09.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:12.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It gets pretty chilly at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I forgot my lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:44.58,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He saw me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:49.17,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He's from Mayama's company, he'll figure\Nout that this is Mayama's coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:47.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:50.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. I thought I'd lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:52.09,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? I'm so uncool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:54.05,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I smooth this over?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:00.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, will you accompany me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:04.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to talk to you about payments, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:06.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:08.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:11.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I should get my coat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:22.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-san, do you prefer soba or udon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:25.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Soba, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:26.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Soba, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:28.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a good place then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little far, so I'll go by highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:33.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:38.14,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up going out wearing Mayama's coat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:43.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells like Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:46.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The scent of other people is mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.36,0:11:50.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he wears anything special, like cologne...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:52.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:56.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The scent of his shampoo, laundry detergent...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And a little bit of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be tobacco...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asleep this whole time so I wasn't aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:17.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:18.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in Tateshina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:21.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And that lake that we can see outside is Lake Megami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:22.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-Tateshina?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:25.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess it's in the Nagano prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here once for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:29.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go ahead and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:32.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The soba here is really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:35.95,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\be1\t(\fs16\bord1.3)\fscy90\fscx80\fsp3\3c&HE6E1DB&\c&H3F3D37&\shad0\move(545,228,517,231)}Fresh Soba
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:36.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:42.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, soba? That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:46.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're having soba for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\bord1.5\fscx65\fs26\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(234,334)\c&H5A9FD2&}"Miwako-san,\N\h\hwhat is that? Is it meat?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:48.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why a souvenir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:53.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you went with Mayama to go get the\Npotteries at Hamabi yesterday, Nomiya...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:55.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It says "Tateshina" on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:57.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:58.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:01.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:05.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that you went to Nagano with Nomiya-san last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:09.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do such a thing out of the blue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:12.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked if I wanted to eat soba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:16.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that it would be a soba restaurant nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But then I got into his car...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:20.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:23.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And... I fell asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-You fell asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In a car driven by a guy that you don't really know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that dangerous man's car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:33.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you always so naïve?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:37.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't show an opening so easily in\Nfront of people you don't know very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:38.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:45.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what? It's none of your business what I do, Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ayu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:47.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The heels on western boots are dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:51.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:52.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Mayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:58.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-san said that she doesn't care about you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:04.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Youngsters these days give up on things\Nat the most inconvenient times...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:08.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:08.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\shad0\bord0\fs11.5\fsp-1\pos(525,236)\c&H4E6265&}Ceramics Dept.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:08.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\fnArial\fscx70\fsp-1\shad0\bord0\pos(616,434)\c&H5D615C&}Inflammable
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:08.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\fnArial\fscx70\fsp-1.5\shad0\bord0\c&H787D8E&\pos(694,440)}Flammable
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:14.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:16.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:31.52,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3a&H64&\bord0.1\be1\shad0\fs43\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\i1\frx10\fry5\c&H1B1E1D&\3c&H293036&\pos(730,114)\frz6.992}Yamada\NLiquor Store
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:17.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:23.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so your family runs a liquor store, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:25.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come buy something later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:28.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, good luck with the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:31.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, the coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:35.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return it to Mayama for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:43.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-kun, the tea! The tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:48.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor... what happened to Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:52.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should leave her alone for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole time he must've been snickering at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:58.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:03.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate Mayama and that guy... I hate everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:04.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:08.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-san got one hell of an in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:09.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too protective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:10.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Give her a little more space...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:17.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-san is a grown adult now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:18.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, please do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have some of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:28.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you freshmen! Return to your stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:29.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring gifts without my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in the middle of her work right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:34.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have some business with her, put it through me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:38.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Scat, scat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:39.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:42.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I look away for just one second...! Stupid brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:46.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:54.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, Rika mentioned that she saw you a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:56.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:00.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she said during the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:02.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it have been at Hibiya Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:04.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was her, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:10.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't seen her since you quit working there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:12.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How long has it been now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:15.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But Rika noticed you as well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen her face in over a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:22.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was to meet her suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd probably force myself onto her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Force yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:28.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, you b-beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:30.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:34.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but maybe that's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:38.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than having this standstill continue,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:42.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,it might bring a chance to the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:45.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Rika doesn't like it, then I'm sure she'll punch you and flee...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't take any rash actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:52.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cool my head as I go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:59.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One moonlit night, in the summer of two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:04.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I carried her to her bed after she collapsed\Nin the shower after work...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:07.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And just spent several hours looking up at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:12.31,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Is her painkiller wearing off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika-san, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:18.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:23.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was having a scary dream, Harada-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:27.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad that you're by my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:31.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:37.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As she awoke from her dream, her eyes\Nbecame more and more transparent...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:41.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time in my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the sound of someone's heart being crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:50.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:55.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Asai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:59.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it really surprised me to hear that\Nyou've been admitted to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:04.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I've shocked Rika-kun as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:10.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's taken care of all the preparations,\Nregistrations, and my treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:14.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very thankful, since I don't have any family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here today as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:20.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her to run an errand for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:22.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:44.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:53.99,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}toganai tsuyogari uso de nurikatameta heya
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:53.99,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I looked up at the night sky after slipping away
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:56.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will his hospitalization last a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:58.75,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}nukedashite miageta yozora
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:58.75,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}From that room painted over with my lies and dull bluffs...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:56.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:03.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika-san, will you let me work for Harada Design again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:09.42,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}yojireta kanaami o itsumo no you ni tobikoete
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:09.42,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}Jumping over the bent chain-link fence like always,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:08.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can be of more use now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:14.34,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}katai hodo wo kakete iku
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:14.34,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}I run on the hard pavement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:14.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that Fujiwara Design is a good company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:19.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's full of young people and works swiftly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:26.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With Asai-san's assistance, I've been able to finish all\Nthe jobs that have been asked of Harada Design.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:33.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So now I want to have the opportunity to take care of Asai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:39.99,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}nitenai bokura wa hosoi ito de tsunagatte iru
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:39.99,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}The two of us, so dissimilar, are connected by a slender thread...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:45.04,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}yoku aru akai yatsu ja naku
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:45.04,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}Though it's not the common red one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:45.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried my hardest to stay away from her, to avoid her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:52.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that if I approached her again without adequate words,\Nshe'd just increase the distance between us again, like now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:55.39,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}ochiatta basho wa ookina ki mo zawameki yande
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:55.39,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}The place we met was quiet, with even the rustling of the large trees still.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:56.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:20:02.93,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}futari no kokyuu no todake ga shimite iku
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:20:02.93,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The air was permeated with only the sound of our breaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:04.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:10.69,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kimi to asobu daremo inai shigaichi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:10.69,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I play with you in the deserted district...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:07.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:11.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer do I have to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:18.32,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}me to me ga au tabi warau
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:18.32,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And we laugh everytime our eyes meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:26.04,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}yoru o kakete iku ima wa utanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:26.04,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're running through the night, please don't shoot us just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:24.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drive you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:37.72,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}horobi no sadame yabutte kakete iku
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:37.72,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}Breaking our doomed fate, we run...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:33.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get this car?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:35.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rental car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:37.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You borrowed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:38.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your motorcycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:40.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ride it in this rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pick it up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:43.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:49.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-kun... you're going the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:51.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me drive for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking advantage of her immobility...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.82,0:20:58.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My selfish self takes the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:03.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The wiper stirs up my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:08.37,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}yoru o kakete iku ima wa utanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:08.37,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}We're running through the night, please don't shoot us just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:05.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And repeats its dull sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:07.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:18.05,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}tooku no akari no hou e kakete iku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:18.05,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}Towards the far-off light, we run...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:15.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Amidst the orange lights, I was slowly sliding\Ndown the large spiral of Daikoku Pier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:28.10,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}waratta kao ni tsukekomare
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:28.10,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}Taken advantage of by his smiling face
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:31.27,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kuchi ni shita sake ni aorarete, oh
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:31.27,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Stimulated by the alcohol she drank
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:34.23,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sora misereta toki ururunda face
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:34.23,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The tear that wells up when she's shown otherwise
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:37.95,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}ki ga sukkari sono ki ni natteru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:37.95,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}She'd alredy become all for it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:44.70,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}atama kakaete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:44.70,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}Holding her head
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:46.41,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(400,400)}atama kakaete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:46.41,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(400,400)}Holding her head
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:50.63,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}yume da to omoikonde mo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:50.63,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}Even if she tries to pretend that it was a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:56.42,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}monogataru kare no paper
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:56.42,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}His paper tells a different story
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:22:02.01,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(400,400)}shiroku samete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:22:02.01,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(400,400)}Becoming white and discolored
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:07.39,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}kumo no ue nobori
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:07.39,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}Ascending above the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:13.69,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,gin iro natsu tsunda yoru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:13.69,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The silvery summer's night she was picked up on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:28.29,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}shimetsukerareru mistake kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:28.29,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}She's being constricted by a mistake that won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.83,0:22:33.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: The moon is calling for her.
